      "description": "Well-kept, good-condition vehicle that presents nicely overall and should appeal to a buyer looking for a solid, usable example. It shows normal cosmetic wear consistent with age and regular use, with minor blemishes and imperfections you would expect on a vehicle that has been driven and enjoyed. Overall, it appears cared for, offers a clean presentation, and should make a satisfying choice for someone wanting a dependable, good-quality car rather than a flawless showpiece.",
