    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Dependable transportation at an affordable price, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers seeking budget-conscious value. It shows cosmetic wear consistent with age and use, but it offers a straightforward ownership opportunity for commuting, light-duty driving, or as an extra vehicle. Priced to sell and represented honestly, this is a sensible option for someone who values function and affordability.",
