    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it starts, moves, and could make a handy cheap runabout, first project, or parts donor. If you\u2019re after something affordable and don\u2019t mind giving it a bit of TLC, this could be a great buy. Priced to sell and open to sensible interest.",
      "price": 3950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project-platform with good bones and plenty of upside for the right buyer. The powertrain fires up, pulls through the rev range, and the chassis feels like a workable foundation for a budget daily, shop truck, or weekend wrenching build. Not a showpiece, but it presents as an honest driver with the kind of mechanical simplicity that makes maintenance straightforward. Expect cosmetic wear and age-related imperfections, yet it still offers practical utility and a strong value proposition compared with over-priced fixer-uppers. If you want an affordable entry point into ownership with room to improve, this one makes a compelling case.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car. Honest poor-condition beater priced to move. First serious buyer wins.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with stories in its sheet metal and plenty of life left for the right owner, this is the kind of ride that speaks to builders, budget-minded drivers, and anyone who sees possibility where others see a project. It has a rugged, honest presence and the sort of character you just can\u2019t fake\u2014perfect as a fixer-upper, parts source, or dependable around-town companion with a little vision. If you\u2019ve been hunting for an affordable entry point and a machine with personality, this one is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable, straightforward, and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for buyers seeking dependable transportation at a budget-friendly price. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who values value over perfection, but it still offers a solid opportunity as an economical daily driver, backup vehicle, or project. Priced to reflect its condition while remaining a strong value in today\u2019s market, this is a chance to get behind the wheel without overspending.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a great opportunity for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a budget-friendly runabout, or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s the kind of honest car you can buy without breaking the bank, and with a little care, it could serve its next owner well. Priced to reflect its condition and offer solid value.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project with honest wear and plenty of upside. Starts, runs, and offers a strong mechanical foundation for someone who wants an affordable driver or weekend fixer-upper. The powertrain feels willing, the chassis is straightforward to work on, and it has the kind of usable character that makes these worth saving. Cosmetically it shows its age, but for the right buyer this is a budget-friendly entry point with real potential. Priced to move and well suited to someone who values function, simplicity, and the chance to improve it over time.",
